</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>After reading the responses, let me point out that the problem with Wizs isn't that they are overpowered - as the pro-Wiz camps seems to defend. The "root" of the problem with Wizs is the stakes involved in the PvP conflict. The ease with which groups of naked Wizs can roll the dice with no downside. Check out my post on NAKED MURDER for a solution.

<P>Ciao...
